{"tid":1432758,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"記者朋友們 聽夠er sir講廢話就入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-08T10:09:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T07:20:48.000Z","uid":285367,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ae2662ab287fb8077b6639374769b92476073d35","tid":1432758,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:09:43.000Z","msg":"睇左幾日記者會 小弟可以大致留意到幾個特別Pattern<br />\n<br />\n1. 警察已經習得<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">遊花園之術</span></strong></span>(但未精) 所以好多時答第一次會跟足稿<br />\n    但係當記者再<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">追問</span></span>/引起記者<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鼓譟</span></span>既時候就會開始出現漏洞 <br />\n    例如尋日O記李sir前言不對後語 一問到<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">老妨</span></span>就開始口啞<br />\n    手足們可以留意到 始終呢班唔係政棍 當問到佢地理虧既時候 會好明顯窒左窒<br />\n    例如<span style=\"color: brown;\">過期煙 </span><br />\n    <br />\n    建議: <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">多用追問</span></strong></span> 但係唔可以太鼓譟 一鼓譟就有位比主持入(我下面會講)<br />\n             香港記者比較習慣一問一答形式 而咁樣係完全chok唔到佢地答野<br />\n             詳情可留意依加黑警係點同市民/示威者講野 <br />\n<br />\n2. 當有危機時就會拋個波比<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>親中媒體記者</strong></span></span> 化解危機<br />\n    以上講緊既危機例如係頭先講既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鼓譟/記者問中左戲肉/記者再三追問</span></span>等等<br />\n    主持會以已經答左為由將發言權交比下一位記者發問 而呢位記者大多數會係<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>親中媒體代表 </strong></span></span><br />\n    今日 尋日都可以見到主持一有時就交下一條比<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">TVB/TVB Pearl</span></span><br />\n<br />\n    建議: 記住 呢個係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記者會</span></span> 係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記者</span></span>既主場 唔好比主持帶領住節奏 <br />\n             問左而對方未答既 請<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>再三追問</strong></span></span></span> 請記住 記者既工作係要由講者口中攞到需要既資訊 <br />\n          一日未有 一日都有必要再問 <br />\n             <br />\n             另外 唔知各位記唔記得 中學雞時候既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>中英文oral</strong></span></span><br />\n             最叻既就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">I agree with you</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後講兩句上位發言者既說話<br />\n             同樣方法可用於主持成功解圍 將發言權交比下位記者時<br />\n             如果上位記者有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">問中戲肉</span></span>/<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">問左大部份記者想知既答案</span> </span><br />\n             下位記者<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>麻煩重複</strong></span></span>上位記者既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未必需要好詳細問 都知道你地可能<br />\n             有題目數量上限制 只需要輕輕帶過 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">&quot;未回答上位記者關於xxx既問題&quot;</span></span> <br />\n             然後繼續自己既問題就可以<br />\n             咁樣做可以永續記者<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真正想知既問題</span></span> 唔會因為交左比下位記者  <br />\n             就比佢地甩身<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 開始林鄭式<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>極力避開敏感字眼</strong></span></span><br />\n    最佳例子就係今日記者會 完全唔敢講<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">過期煙</span></span><br />\n    比人追問到最後一條 指到明講緊<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">過期煙</span></span>問題<br />\n    都只係敢講 &quot;<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">個啲煙</span></span>&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n    建議: 必須<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>即時更正</strong></span></span>講者提出既字眼 例如佢講個啲煙既時候 就 <br />\n             立即更正佢為過期煙 務求令佢爆響口 再係爆響口其間講錯更多野<br />\n<br />\n4. 倒<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>黑</strong></span>為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>白</strong></span> 極黑就唔提<br />\n    一路將所有警察做既壞事都賴落示威者到 總之警察<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">傷人</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">濫捕</span> </span>都係因為示威者<br />\n  <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">  <span style=\"color: red;\">暴力行為 警察去唔到元朗/北角</span></span> 都係因為示威者 <br />\n    遇到理虧/不利既問題最叻就係講<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">手頭上無資料/我唔係現場/該區同事決定</span></span><br />\n    迴避率 100%<br />\n<br />\n    建議: 我唔係記者唔清楚記者會有咩規矩 但係請記者朋友們答<br />\n             <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記者會可唔可以帶screen入去</span></span>?<br />\n             如果係警察回答唔清楚/無資料既時候 <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>直接比相關事件既影片</strong></span></span>佢睇<br />\n             再<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">追問</span></span>/<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">要求回應</span></span> 會唔會係比較有效阻止佢地迴避既方法<br />\n             有其他方法歡迎提出<br />\n<br />\n記住 政府用記者會呢招 係想將佢地想發放既資訊 每一日透過記者會輸出<br />\n而我地可以<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">反其道而行</span></span> 比市民睇到警察到底係有幾咁<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無能</span></span> 幾咁 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無賴</span></span><br />\n對住鐵證如山既惡行置若罔聞 繼續佢地既<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>&quot;總之所有野都係因為示威者&quot;</strong></span></span>論<br />\n留意到最近既記者會好多時都觸及到重要既點 例如<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">老妨 證物處理 過期煙</span></strong></span><br />\n但係永遠都比警方及時用以上方法化解 真係睇到係螢幕後既我牙癢癢 <br />\n希望聽日記者可以屌打警察 還市民一個公道<br />\n<br />\np.s. 另私心建議民間記者會唔好係警察記者會前開<br />\n       都幾肯定接下嚟會係兩邊記者會既對罵環節<br />\n       先罵個位唔著數"},{"pid":"f9c9589909a5888565f56e07186fed818f9c1c68","tid":1432758,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:09:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5bd0fc0be031a2523c8903c171380709520b26ce","tid":1432758,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:32:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00afc5cdf0c1203ecadf7a74622d7512a57c2e19","tid":1432758,"uid":270577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:34:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b2be02ab7ec21a8277fddcb7d86f4f49d5fea570","tid":1432758,"uid":270577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab032b2418da3066c92f7573251c681ebca76f5","tid":1432758,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:35:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b63e261b5d8f4168c6f7160f614cf736a33c054c","tid":1432758,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:56:35.000Z","msg":"推 記者朋友可以一睇<br />\n希望幫到你地"},{"pid":"59f7bf46e06ed6b158f4af030ccf7a1597b46172","tid":1432758,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae2662ab287fb8077b6639374769b92476073d35","tid":1432758,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:09:43.000Z","msg":"睇左幾日記者會 小弟可以大致留意到幾個特別Pattern<br />\n<br />\n1. 警察已經習得<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">遊花園之術</span></strong></span>(但未精) 所以好多時答第一次會跟足稿<br />\n    但係當記者再<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">追問</span></span>/引起記者<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鼓譟</span></span>既時候就會開始出現漏洞 <br />\n    例如尋日O記李sir前言不對後語 一問到<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">老妨</span></span>就開始口啞<br />\n    手足們可以留意到 始終呢班唔係政棍 當問到佢地理虧既時候 會好明顯窒左窒<br />\n    例如<span style=\"color: brown;\">過期煙 </span><br />\n   